name: boolean/Reverse condition
description:
Turns binary independent signals into a boolean.

Example A:
1. null@0 is received via `true`
2. true@0 is sent via `boolean`

Example B:
1. "foo"@1 is received via `false`
2. false@1 is sent via `boolean`
